divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving west on 4th. In the space above the street I saw a bright yellow-gold light moving at a very high rate of speed moving south to north. Too fast to be any sort of plane, but traveling parallel to the ground. I only saw it for a short time due to the trees and it's speed.
